		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I discovered another game has the same anomaly: Nintendo's mahjong
<br />And the FDS was launched with 7 games including Zelda (v1.0 of course) and.... Mahjong!!
<br />
<br />So the only two games with that anomaly are among the 7 initial releases
<br />
<br />Obviously an error form the devs who forgot to use the BCD "year of showa" format in those initial releases.

		

